    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-08-02T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-08-02T10:00:00-05:00" n="743"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d743">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.1531/95: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Keena</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-08-02T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 2, 1935—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>33. Your telegram No. 37, July 29, 6 p.m. The Department agrees with you that
                    time may be saved if this Government now submits a tentative final draft of the
                    agreement and this is accordingly being prepared. It will be sent you by air
                    mail as soon as it is completed.</p>
                <p>The telegraphic reply prepared to your 36, July 22, 6 p.m.,<note n="22"
                        xml:id="d743fn22">Not printed.</note> will not be sent. The suggestions
                    embodied therein as well as in section <pb facs="0839" n="746" xml:id="pg_746"/>
                    1 of your 37, July 29, 6 p.m., will be incorporated in the tentative draft.</p>
                <p>We assume you do not intend to present separately the changes in the general
                    provisions outlined in instruction 712 of July 20<note n="25" xml:id="d743fn25"
                        >Not printed.</note> but will take them up with the Honduran Government en
                    bloc together with the other points on which agreement has not been reached when
                    the final draft reaches you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
